attributes.review: I downloaded this app to see what trump was about, but once it downloaded, it opened and logged me right out. I kept trying to click it, but nothing happened, but then my phone shut completely off. This has never happened before and my phone is fairly new. Once my phone turned on again, all my apps were glitchy and everything was so laggy. Not even my texts would send. This app is terrible, it has some sort of virus once you download it. Unless you want a virus, I recommend downloading it.

attributes.title: He drowned my fish!!😡🤯🐠
attributes.review: I downloaded this app in hopes of learning more about the amazing orange Cheeto man😘, but instead, once I opened the app I was greeted with a horrifying Karen parade singing “ReAl WoMeN VoTe FoR TrUmP” and other similar tunes. Of course I was in favor of the initial message, but out of nowhere a group of headless power rangers were holding the flaming body of our beloved Donald. I was screaming to let him go but they preceded. They set him in the middle of the Karen circle and joined hands with the Karen’s shouting “kill the fish!” Of course at this moment I quickly turned to look at my fish who was sunbathing on the sand of his tank, only to see him shortly after levitate and float above his pool! Immediately he was pushed under the water and began suffocating!!! I tried to move to help him, but as soon as I jumped off my bed, a group of armadillos rushed through my door and held me down. I was able to break one of my arms free and delete the app, but sadly my fish was dead. -1020393474929/10 recommended DO NOT DOWNLOAD!!!! Also, it took FIVE WEEKS to download. Do not download or  You will have a similar experience.
